data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!!Welcome to your recently upgraded four-bedroom, three-bathroom home in scenic Riverview, Florida! As you enter, you are greeted with high vaulted ceilings in an open floor plan on the first floor. Receiving guests is exciting as you have a formal dining room, family room, and a living room to enjoy time together as well as a half bath. The kitchen has upgraded granite counter tops, upgraded longer cabinets, 18in tiles, laminate vinyl flooring in living room, new dishwasher(2021), new microwave (2023), new washer and dryer (2023), as well as freshly painted interior throughout in 2022, archways, making daily chores a breeze and family gatherings delightful! Double sliding glass doors leads you to the screened-in porch where you can enjoy peaceful evenings overlooking a beautiful serene lake view! As you make your way upstairs to the second floor, you will find a split floor plan with a small loft area leading to each bedroom. The primary suite has a bonus sitting area you can transform into what your heart desires! Whether it is an office, nursery, or sitting area, it adds a uniqueness to your already spacious master with a walk-in closet and a nice size master bathroom! You will also find 3 more bedrooms and a second full bathroom. Enjoy the hot days in the community pool where you also have a clubhouse and playground. Entrance of community lays right on 301 where you have lots of shopping centers, restaurants, an emergency room, plus more for easy commute for anything and everything you need! With a spacious layout and these recent upgrades, this home is the perfect blend of modern convenience and tranquility. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to call it your own!
